<p id="fs-idm128894672">12</p></div></div>
<div data-type="exercise" id="fs-idm68696640"><div data-type="problem" id="fs-idm10527280">
<p id="fs-idm167401120">Which of the following equations describe particle-like behavior? Which describe wavelike behavior? Do any involve both types of behavior? Describe the reasons for your choices.</p>
<p id="fs-idp41728">(a) <em data-effect="italics">c</em> = <em data-effect="italics">&#955;&#957;</em></p>
